here today to lend his voice

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:10.620
to this worldwide celebration
of innovation, copyright

00:07:10.620 --> 00:07:14.090
and how it changes
and improves lives.

00:07:14.090 --> 00:07:19.510
Please join me in welcoming
Representative Doug Collins.

00:07:19.510 --> 00:07:28.050
