00:08:12.060 --> 00:08:14.490
You just saw on the screen,
you've heard about it

00:08:14.490 --> 00:08:16.770
as how things have changed
lives, that creative spark,

00:08:16.770 --> 00:08:20.050
that creative use that changes
lives but I am going to come at it

00:08:20.050 --> 00:08:23.450
from just a little bit different
