carry on sometimes when I was down.

00:10:50.070 --> 00:10:53.440
I found the hope to say
there's something better

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:55.330
and that there's ways that
we can improve our lives.

00:10:55.330 --> 00:10:58.700
I found in books and music, I
found the ability to cross oceans

00:10:58.700 --> 00:11:01.460
