00:21:35.020 --> 00:21:39.310
It gives the creator the power
to determine when, where,

00:21:39.310 --> 00:21:44.650
and how their creative genius can
be used by others and importantly,

00:21:44.650 --> 00:21:47.430
to get compensated for that use.

00:21:47.430 --> 00:21:52.080
