from the time that work is created

00:21:52.080 --> 00:21:56.300
and recorded in some tangible
form regardless of whether

00:21:56.300 --> 00:22:01.970
that work is registered or any
formal action has been taken.

00:22:01.970 --> 00:22:05.460
